Ext.data.JsonP['Modifying_Your_Configuration']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Modifying Your Configuration</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-29004871\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Modifying Your Configuration</h1>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-29004871_ModifyingYourConfiguration-Overview\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Overview</span></h2>\n    <p>This guide explains the steps for modifying your configuration file.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-29004871_ModifyingYourConfiguration-ModifyingtheINIConfigurationFile\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Modifying the INI Configuration File</span></h2>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Locate the INI configuration file:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Mac OS X</strong>:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Navigate to the <tt class=\" \">/Applications/Appcelerator Studio</tt> folder in Finder.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Right-click (or control-click) on <tt class=\" \">AppceleratorStudio.app</tt> and choose Show package contents.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>In the new Finder window navigate to <tt class=\" \">Contents/MacOS</tt>.    </p>\n</li></ol></li><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Windows</strong>: Navigate to the location of your Studio application (likely under <tt class=\" \">C:\\Users\\username\\AppData\\Local\\Appcelerator Studio</tt>)    </p>\n</li></ol></li><li class=\" \">    <p>Open <tt class=\" \">AppceleratorStudio.ini</tt>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Edit the options as desired    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Save and close the file    </p>\n</li></ol>    <p>    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n            <p>You can follow the same procedures on Eclipse. The folder structure will be identical but the file to edit is <strong class=\" \">eclipse.ini</strong>.    </p>\n    </div>\n        </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=29004871\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Modifying Your Configuration"});